{"tid":2493969,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《火影忍者》動畫導演患癌不治去世 享年57歲","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T19:31:34.000Z","uid":4618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc72346070fcfd9f22524e041bb851e16e3ed5ba","tid":2493969,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/osamukoba/status/1383583055521017858?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fosamukoba%2Fstatus%2F1383583055521017858%3Fs%3D21&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RHT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=9edba3c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fosamukoba%2Fstatus%2F1383583055521017858%3Fs%3D21&h=eccbb722\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/osamukoba/status/1383583055521017858?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n4月18日，今天官方推特公布了這個沉痛的消息：「小林治，57歲，昨晚去了天國。從2年前就開始和腎臟癌鬥爭了，但很遺憾已經精疲力盡了&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n此前，其官方推特已經3個多月沒有更新。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，小林治大約2年前罹患腎臟癌，一直處於艱辛抗爭病魔中，此前其推文寫道：「遺憾的是我還有很多未了之事，只盼來生再創作出優秀的作品吧。」<br />\n<br />\n小林治於昨夜去世，享年57歲，曾擔任《火影忍者疾風傳》《BECK》《魔法使的條件：夏之空》的監督，也曾參與《天元突破紅蓮螺巖》《多羅羅2019版》等諸多作品。"},{"pid":"723607eccc4b7a7bcbfb967ffe39f12ca930642c","tid":2493969,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"多羅羅都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b4ad4496734ead9c3f62e31f9861aacf7e0aeb","tid":2493969,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"動漫界高質製作人越嚟越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78313162052fa4c286744db6ddfeeb2af90c9ec","tid":2493969,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b4ad4496734ead9c3f62e31f9861aacf7e0aeb","tid":2493969,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"動漫界高質製作人越嚟越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite